#

Orange Vinaigrette Dressing

5 min
$2.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

DressingVinaigretteHealthy

Description

A refreshing and vibrant dressing perfect for salads or drizzling over grilled vegetables.

Ingredients

  • fresh orange juice: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 1/2 cup
  • apple cider vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 tablespoon
  • dijon mustard: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
